children.subject: There was a form released for 16B last week -- maybe that's what you're thinking of? If you're taking 16A over the summer, fill out the above form. If you're taking 16B over the summer fill out their form @12347.
Yes. Thank you I missed the A. Sorry.
Wasn’t a similar form regarding lab kits release a week ago? I’m guessing everyone should still fill out this form.

Yes, we've moved that section to MW for scheduling reasons, and I'm sorry for an inconvenience it's caused. Please choose the lab section time that works best for you, it doesn't matter if it corresponds to the time that you're currently registered for. We expect almost everyone will be in either their first or second choice section.
I’m currently enrolled in a lab section that’s tue/thu 5-8 but that option is not on the form. Have the sections changed?
Yes -- please fill out the form ASAP!
I just enrolled in the class. Is it possible for me to still get the lab kits and have it shipped?
Can we still pick up our lab kits this week as scheduled? I know the form said 1:30-2:30 pm Monday-Friday this week but I haven't seen anything confirming this. Thanks!

history.content:
Hello EECS 16A students,

 

Labs are an important part of EECS 16A, and we’re working hard to make the remote lab experience both fun and educational. Please fill out this form by Friday, June 5 to sign up for a lab section and reserve your lab kit.

UPDATE: The form is still open to reserve your lab kit! (Lab sections will be assigned for those who did not fill out the form by 6/5/20)

  1. Sign up for a lab section! To get credit for the lab, you’ll need to get checked off by a lab TA during your section, so it’s important that you’re able to attend virtually. Therefore, we’re opening two new lab sections, and we want you to choose the one that’s right for you.

  2. Reserve your lab kit! We will distribute kits out of Cory Hall to all students who can pick them up. If you need a kit shipped to you there will be no questions asked, but please help conserve shipping resources for the students who need them.

Everything can be done in this form. It only takes 3 min, so fill it out as soon as possible, and tell your friends who are also in the class. If you do not fill out the form we cannot give you a kit and you will be unable to complete the labs!

We’re very excited for the summer and looking forward to meeting all of you!

Urmita, Panos, and Grace
